    Page: 109
By: Hermes
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Snare of Woman
---
He who falls into the snares of women is like a bird that falls into the
hands of a little silly child; the child plays with it merrily and is glad,
but meanwhile the bird endures the pains of death, and undergoes all manner
of tortures.
